balizing world, and great mayors are already proving that this is so.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 0aComparative government. 0aLeadership. 0aLeadershipages. 0aMayors -- Case studies. 0aMayorsvCase studies. 0aMunicipal government. 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / History & Theory.2bisacsh08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013z978311053799440uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030016483140uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300164831423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300164831/original  a978-3-11-053799-4  Yale University Press Backlist eBook-Package 2000-2013c2000d2013  aEBA_FAO  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles